Subject: [PATCHv5 3/6] drm/msm: rearrange the gpu_rmw() function
Date:   Tue, 22 Sep 2020 11:48:16 +0530
Message-Id: <fc69d5c3a68c11b9d4cb692de76bc8d875062cb8.1600754909.git.saiprakash.ranjan@codeaurora.org>
